## ğŸ—ºï¸ Roadmap

### Current Release: v0.1.37 (In Development)

**Latest Features**:
- âœ… **Extended `/analyze` Workflow**: 5-agent comprehensive analysis (Quill + News Sentry + Macro Lens + Risk Shield + Tax Scout)
- âœ… **`/discover` Workflow**: NEW systematic idea generation (Screen Forge + Quill + Risk Shield)
- âœ… **Progressive Streaming**: Real-time display of sub-agent tool calls as they execute
- âœ… **State Accumulation**: Each agent receives context from previous agents
- âœ… **Workflow Synthesis**: Comprehensive recommendations integrating all perspectives

**Recently Completed** (v0.1.36):
- âœ… **Automatic Intent-Based Routing**: No more manual agent switchingâ€”just ask naturally
- âœ… **Router Agent**: LangGraph tool-calling supervisor coordinating 10 specialist agents
- âœ… **Enhanced Transparency**: Watch router analyze intent and select appropriate agents
- âœ… **Backward Compatible**: All `/command` syntax still works for power users

**Earlier Releases**:
- âœ… **Hedge Smith Agent**: Options strategies (collars, covered calls, puts), Greeks analysis (v0.1.35)
- âœ… **Tax Scout Agent**: Tax-loss harvesting, wash-sale compliance, year-end planning (v0.1.34)
- âœ… **Risk Shield Agent**: Portfolio risk management, VAR, drawdown analysis (v0.1.33)
- âœ… **News Sentry Agent**: Real-time 8-K monitoring, insider tracking, breaking news (v0.1.32)

**Planned for v0.1.38** (Q1 2025):
- [ ] **New Workflows**: `/optimize-tax` (Tax Scout + Hedge Smith), `/protect` (Risk Shield + Hedge Smith)
- [ ] **API Caching Layer**: DuckDB-based caching to reduce API calls and improve performance
- [ ] **Workflow Progress Visualization**: Enhanced TUI display for multi-agent workflows

### Future Releases

**v0.2.0+** (Q2 2025):
- [ ] **Backtesting Engine**: Test investment strategies on historical data
- [ ] **Web UI**: Browser-based interface (in addition to TUI)
- [ ] **State Persistence**: PostgreSQL checkpointer for LangGraph
- [ ] **Cloud Deployment**: LangGraph Cloud integration
- [ ] **Custom Agents**: User-defined agent templates and tools
